<span class='talk-transcript__para__text'>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='719000' id='t-719000'>In the 19th century,</span>
<span class='talk-transcript__fragment' data-time='721000' id='t-721000'>when Muslims were looking at Europe as an example,</span>
